'''Aban Ramḍan''' d argaz asarti azwaw, i gelan d amenzawi deg umezruy n tegrawala n [[Lezzayer]].

== Tudert-is ==
 
Ilul deg 10 yunyu 1920 di taddart [[iεezzuzen]] di tama n [[Larba n at yiraten]], imut deg 1957. D netta i llan d aqerru n tegrawla, u d aserti ugar n ukabar Tirni n Tleli Aγelnaw [[FLN]].

